creator: The Kroger Co.
descriptionHtml:
Looking for a faster, easier, more rewarding shopping experience? Save time and money with the City Market app! It puts convenience, savings and rewards at your fingertips. Simply download the app, create an account and register your City Market Shopper’s Card to access all these great benefits:

- Shop Pickup or Delivery right from the app!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!
descriptionShort: Save with us! Coupons, ads, rewards, find stores & shopping list in one app!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We’re working around the clock to ensure our services and products are available to you. Here are some release highlights:

- Access Kroger Pay from the home screen.
- Turn dark mode on and off in the app settings.
- Minor bugs have been fixed to improve your overall experience.

We value your feedback. If you need help or have a suggestion, please contact our Customer Service Center at 1-800-576-4377.

Looking for a faster, easier, more rewarding shopping experience? Save time and money with the City Market app! It puts convenience, savings and rewards at your fingertips. Simply download the app, create an account and register your City Market Shopper’s Card to access all these great benefits:

- Shop Pickup or Delivery right from the app!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!

creator: The Kroger Co.
descriptionHtml:
Looking for a faster, easier, more rewarding shopping experience? Save time and money with the City Market app! It puts convenience, savings and rewards at your fingertips. Simply download the app, create an account and register your City Market Shopper’s Card to access all these great benefits:

- Shop Pickup or Delivery right from the app!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!

Looking for a faster, easier, more rewarding shopping experience? Save time and money with the City Market app! It puts convenience, savings and rewards at your fingertips. Simply download the app, create an account and register your City Market Shopper’s Card to access all these great benefits:

- Shop Pickup or Delivery right from the app!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!

- Shop Pickup or Delivery right from the app!

- Easily build your online shopping list, and use it to shop in-store or to place your online order.

- View your Weekly Ads and quickly add sale items or specials to your shopping list.

- Load digital coupons directly to your Shopper’s Card and use them to save on items from your shopping list.

- Get even more savings when you choose items from our Smart Suggest feature.

- Refill your City Market Pharmacy prescriptions directly from your phone or tablet. Just type in your prescription number, select your Pharmacy and schedule a convenient pickup time.

- Check your fuel points.

- Use our locator to find the closest City Market store or fuel center.

- View your purchase history. Use it to create standard orders that will save you time.

- Save BIG with exclusive promotions, personalized offers and bonus rewards.

To use the City Market app, you'll need a City Market digital account. You can register for your account and link your Shopper’s Card through the app. If you don't have a Shopper’s Card, you can create one when you register to access all of these savings and rewards!
